# Title: Regedit as Trusted Installer
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2021-05-27
# Level: high
# Description: Detects a regedit started with TrustedInstaller privileges or by ProcessHacker.exe
# MITRE Tactic: Privilege Escalation
# Tags: attack.privilege-escalation, attack.t1548
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_regedit_trustedinstaller.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Unlikely

Image="*\\regedit.exe" ParentImage IN ("*\\TrustedInstaller.exe", "*\\ProcessHacker.exe")